('ETHGlobal - Blockchain Hackathon', 'ETHGlobal', 'hackathon', 'Build decentralized apps on Ethereum and blockchain platforms. Focus on DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, Web3. Access mentors from top blockchain projects.', '2025-04-15', '2025-03-01', '2025-04-15', 'https://ethglobal.com/events', ARRAY['Blockchain development experience', 'Smart contract knowledge', 'Team of 1-5 members', 'Deploy on testnet or mainnet']),
